		<div class="content">
		<br />
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: large;"><strong>“丹桂第一声”中央民族乐团音乐会</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: medium;"> </span><span style="font-size: medium;">时间：<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2013</span>年<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">1</span>月<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">25</span>日</span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">地点：国家大剧院音乐厅</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">指挥：何建国（国家一级指挥）</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">首席：唐峰（国家一级演员）</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">主持：耿靓<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span></span></p>
 
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000;"> <br /></span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">一、民族管弦乐《春节序曲》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                       </span>李焕之曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><br />二、二胡、大提琴与乐队《伦敦德里小调》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                     </span>爱尔兰民歌<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">  </span>赵东升编配</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                        二胡演奏：段超（金钟奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                     大提琴演奏：田维扬（法国布列斯特国际艺术节获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><br />三、唢呐与乐队《渔樵农耕》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                       </span>刘文金曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><br />四、箜篌独奏《梅花三弄》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                 </span>古曲<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">  </span>吴林编曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                 箜篌演奏：吴林</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><br />五、民族管弦乐《火车托卡塔》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                     </span>刘湲曲<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">  </span>姜莹改编</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> <br /></span><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">  <br />   ——————————————<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">     </span>中<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>场<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>休<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>息<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">     </span>——————————————</span><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><br /><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">  <br /></span>六、民族管弦乐《万泉河水清又清》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                       </span>选自舞剧《红色娘子军》主题音乐片段</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                            吴祖强、杜鸣心、戴洪威、施万春、王燕樵曲<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">  </span>李文平编曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><br />七、京剧演唱《对花歌》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                </span>根据京剧《卖水》选段<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">  </span>赵东升编曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                   演唱：储兰兰</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><br />八、笛子与乐队《春到湘江》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                      </span>宁保生曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                    笛子：王次恒（国家一级演员、文化部优秀剧目展演优秀奖获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><br />九、二胡齐奏《赛马》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                           </span>黄海怀曲<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">   </span>陈思昂编配</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                              二胡演奏：李源源等</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><br />十、民族管弦乐《山村的节日》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                  </span>刘文金曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><br />十一、民族管弦乐《关东情》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                                      </span>隋利军曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">*</span>曲目以当天演出为准。<br /><br /><a href="http://www.chncpa.org/ycgp/jmxx/2012-10-29/421734.shtml">国家大剧院=&gt;丹桂第一声</a> <br /><br />订票热线：64933876、66550000</span></p>		</div>

		
			
